00:35:37,138 --> 00:35:40,112
but I'm going to give you
what I consider the best books

623
00:35:40,113 --> 00:35:42,930
to get anyone started on the
path to critical thinking.

624
00:35:44,502 --> 00:35:47,938
First off, everyone in the
world should read Carl Sagan's classic

625
00:35:47,939 --> 00:35:51,729
"The Demon Haunted World:
Science as a Candle in the Dark. "

626
00:35:51,730 --> 00:35:55,343
This book is the magnum opus of
critical thinking for everyone.

627
00:35:55,344 --> 00:35:57,374
It's easy to read,
approachable,

628
00:35:57,375 --> 00:36:00,648
and every page is fascinating
no matter who you are.

