00:36:00,649 --> 00:36:04,164
Chapter 12 includes Sagan's
famous Baloney Detection Kit,

630
00:36:04,165 --> 00:36:06,539
quite possibly the handiest Swiss army knife

631
00:36:06,540 --> 00:36:08,850
for understanding our universe.

632
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:15,979
The second book is Flim Flam,
