00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:03,919
shocking exposés of human weaknesses,

648
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:08,122
driven by superstition, racism,
greed, and ignorance.

649
00:37:08,123 --> 00:37:10,771
If you think James
Randi pulls no punches,

650
00:37:10,772 --> 00:37:13,420
try re-reading Mark
Twain with new eyes.

651
00:37:15,854 --> 00:37:18,200
Finally, I'm going to recommend
my own book,

652
00:37:18,201 --> 00:37:21,296
Skeptoid, Critical
Analysis of Pop Phenomena,

